comments.content: It’s one of Ray Larabie’s old freebies called [Kenyan Coffee Bold](http://web.archive.org/web/20080406143851/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/larabie/kenyan-coffee/). Horizontally stretched and/or vertically squashed (I just tested this myself).
